    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2625393>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Lateral (A), ventral (B) and dorsal (C) views of the head of Amphisbaena mebengokre sp. nov. (holotype, MNRJ 25189). Scale bar = 2 millimeters." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2625393/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2625395>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Ventral view of cloacal region and tail of Amphisbaena mebengokre sp. nov. (holotype, MNRJ 25189). The arrow points to two precloacals pores. Scale bar = 2 millimeters." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2625395/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2625397>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Amphisbaena mebengokre sp. nov. (holotype, MNRJ 25189). (A) Dorsal and (B) general ventral view. Scale bar = 5 millimeters." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2625397/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2625399>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Geographic distribution of Amphisbaenia silvestrii group based in present study material and bibliographic data (Gans 1962, 1964a; Vanzolini 1991, 1997; Mott & Vieites 2009; Silva Jr et al. 2009; Valdujo et al. 2009; Vrcibradic 1999; and Santos et al. 2014). Brazilian states: DF: Distrito Federal, GO: Goiás, MG: Minas Gerais, MT: Mato Grosso, MS: Mato Grosso do Sul, and TO: Tocantins." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2625399/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2625401>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Phylogenetic relationships of Amphisbaena mebengokre sp. nov. within Amphisbaena based in the maximum likelihood (ML) tree produced in RAxML of Amphisbaenia on combined analysis of three nuclear (BDNF, c-mos and RAG1) and three mitocondrial (12S, 16S and ND2) markers. Red branches denotes the clade composed by species of the Amphisbaena silvestrii group. The values of boostrap> 70% are showed in the nodes." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2625401/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

